		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p><addressee>Rev Mr. Leeser</addressee>  <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Albany</placeName> <add>&#63;</add> <date>March 22 5610</date> A M<add>&#63;</add></p>
				<p>Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I am very sorry&#44; that it was impossible<lb/> for me to go via <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> to <placeName>New York</placeName>&#44; I<lb/> went by steamer from <placeName>Charleston</placeName> to <placeName>New York</placeName>.<lb/>  I am elected in <placeName>Charleston</placeName>&#44; and I shall leave <placeName>Albany</placeName><lb/> the <date>15th of April</date>.  I hope to do much good there&#44;<lb/> for the people listened very attentively to my words.<lb/>  I shall have now time enough to write&#44; and I am<lb/> sure I will write now more for the Occident and<lb/> also for the Asmonean than the respective Editors<lb/> will feel inclined to publish.  I had yet not<lb/> time to collect the money for the occident&#44; but I shall<lb/> do it as soon as possible.</p>
				<p>I think&#44; since I turned a <sic>portuguise</sic> jew&#44; you are bound<lb/> to cheer me with two <add>Hebrew</add> of this <add>Hebrew</add> one for me&#44;<lb/> and one for my wife.</p>
				<p>I found the occident in almost every house in <placeName>Charleston</placeName>&#44;<lb/> and it was chiefly through its columns&#44; that I was<lb/> recommended to the people&#44; for which I am very<lb/> grateful to you.</p>
				<p><persName>Dr. Raphael</persName> is an orator&#44; a poet&#44; an original<lb/> <sic>geneius</sic>&#59; but no scholar as I thought him to be.<lb/>  There is much in his lectures that could be <sic>criticised</sic>&#44; but I have no desire to do it&#44; since I doubt&#44; that<lb/> any good can result of it.</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>I will write you more next&#44; for now <sic>recieve</sic><lb/> the assurance of my best friendship</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)">Yours</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)"><persName role="author">Dr Wise</persName></p>
			<pb n="2V"/>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(6)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(6)"><placeName>Walnut St.</placeName></p>
